Generate a professional report for multiple invoices with the following requirements:

1. For each invoice:
   - Vendor Name
   - Invoice Number
   - Invoice Date
   - Itemized Table including:
       • Item Description
       • Quantity
       • Unit Price
       • Amount
       • Tax (if applicable)
   - Subtotal, Tax, and Grand Total clearly shown.

2. Create a summary section at the end of the report:
   - Total amount per invoice
   - Combined grand total across all invoices

3. Draft a professional email:
   - Include a clear summary of all invoices
   - List all items with their prices
   - Display the total amount at the end
   - Use a formal tone suitable for business communication

Output format:
- Report in **table format** (Word or PDF ready)
- Email in **business format** (ready to copy-paste or send)
